race.comment: APOCALYPTIC (1) looks to have the G2 Light Fingers right at her mercy. She reunites with Berry and they return to the scene of their G2 Furious triumph to kick off last spring. Two strong trials have her spot-on and she's drawn the A1. She is clearly the one to beat. SAVVY HALLIE (2) chased soundly into fourth when resuming in The Sunlight at the Gold Coast and has been kept fresh since. Worth remembering she won the G2 Silver Shadow second-up here in the spring. She should land alongside APOCALYPTIC in the run and her fitness edge could count for plenty. KARINSKA (4) resumes over what may be short of her best trip, but she gets McDonald and a soft draw - that alone demands inclusion. WOOTTON LASS (9) was electric in her recent trial and should burn across to give plenty of cheek. A knockout hope at big odds. ARTISTIC VENTURE (3) also resumes off two solid trials, though the wide draw will make life tricky.
